Our Services

Indian Flowers and Strings

Enhance your spiritual rituals with a beautiful selection of Indian flowers and essential pooja items. From the vibrant marigold and fragrant jasmine to the sacred lotus, these flowers bring color and fragrance to your ceremonies. Complement them with traditional pooja items like diyas, incense sticks, kumkum, and others to create a serene and auspicious atmosphere.

Housewarming Flower Arrangement

Welcome warmth and joy into your new home with this vibrant housewarming flower arrangement. Featuring a delightful mix of fresh blooms in cheerful colors, its the perfect way to celebrate new beginnings and create a cozy, inviting atmosphere.

Wedding Garlands

Enhance the beauty and tradition of your wedding with our exquisite Indian marriage garlands. Handcrafted with fresh, vibrant flowers like roses, jasmine, and marigolds, these garlands symbolize love, purity, and prosperity. Perfect for traditional ceremonies, our garlands are meticulously designed to add a touch of elegance and cultural significance to your special day. Available in various styles and colors, each garland is a work of art, ensuring your wedding is as memorable and beautiful as youve always dreamed.

Temple Services

Flower services to Indian temples with fresh flowers, garlands, and pooja items is a practice that combines devotion, tradition, and meticulous care.

We at Ponmani Florist meticulously care and follow our tradition when we serve flowers to temples.

About Us

PONMANI Florist&nbsp;provides the highest quality, freshest Indian flowers for a variety of floral needs. From wedding garlands crafted with precision and care to vibrant pooja garlands and elegant Jasmine and Mullai strings. The team at Ponmani Florist is dedicated to creating unique, beautiful floral compositions for every occasion.

In addition to our beautiful flowers, we provide a comprehensive range of pooja items, such as diyas, incense sticks, kumkum, idols, and sandalwood paste, ensuring you have everything you need for your spiritual practices. Our products are carefully selected to maintain the highest quality and authenticity, helping you create a serene and auspicious atmosphere for your rituals.

Whether you are preparing for a festival, a wedding, or a simple daily prayer, our online shop is your one-stop destination for all things sacred and beautiful.
